text=Dear Zargh,$B$BThe steaks you sent are fine.  Well marbled, thickly sliced and packed in boar fat.  They're just how I like them.  When I eat them later, I will think of you as I gnaw on the last bits of bone and grisle.  I will close my eyes and see your strong, scarred hands chopping and cutting...$B$BHah!  That reminds me of when you had your accident and lost a finger... Oh, Zargh!  Thinking of that day makes me giggle like a little girl.$B$BYou're so cute when you're bleeding!$B$B-Gryshka

